  "description": "<p>We are hiring for our software project for providing application support role in banking environment</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualification &amp; Responsibilites</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>University Degree in Computer Science or Equivalent.</li>\n  <li><strong>At least 6 years of experience performing system support and java programming with Java/J2EE/JSP/MS SQL/Oracle</strong></li>\n  <li>Advantageous to have experience in supporting banking applications, IBM FileNet/Content Navigator/Case Manager, Suntec Pricing and Product Bundling</li>\n  <li><strong>Deployment of applications or patches in IBM WebSphere Application Server.</strong></li>\n  <li>Familiar with Windows, AIX Servers commands.</li>\n  <li><strong>Hands-on working knowledge of Microsoft SQL and Oracle.</strong></li>\n  <li>Good in troubleshooting production issues.</li>\n  <li>Working knowledge of JIRA, GITHUB, Eclipse.</li>\n  <li>Very good communication skills and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Vendor Management Experience</li>\n</ul>",
